{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_52_03",
  "title": "小美山愛 3話 脳天を突き刺すようなかぐわしい香り",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "……さん、{user}さん！\n良かった、目が覚めたんですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…san‚ {user}-san!\nThank goodness‚ you're awake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.3960770289
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "愛？　……そうか、俺は……崖から落ちて……\n愛が助けてくれたんだな……ありがとう。……痛っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "AI? …That's right‚ I… fell off the cliff…\nAI saved me… thank you. …Ouch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "いつものスーツも革靴もズタボロになっちゃって……\nそれに……足をひねったみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your usual suit and leather shoes are all in tatters…\nAnd… Looks like you sprained your ankle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.0820171993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "急には動かないで下さい\n応急手当はしてありますから、大丈夫ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't make any sudden movements\nI've given you first aid‚ so you'll be fine",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0486838659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.8373456956
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ちっきしょう！　こんな所で……！　ここまでか……\n俺は足手まといになる。……先に行ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Damn it! In a place like this…! Is this all the way…\nI'll be a burden. …Go first",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "……嫌です。こんな所に置いてなんて行けません\nほら、私の背中に掴まって下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No. I can't leave you here\nCome on‚ hold on to my back",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0358491899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.5342168174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "約束したじゃないですか。二人で『DENSETSU』\nに辿り着いて、一緒にラーメンを食べようって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We promised‚ right? We'd reach \"DENSETSU\"\nand eat ramen together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.4648288412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "きっとどんなに美味しいラーメンだって\n二人一緒じゃないと、美味しくありませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how delicious the ramen is‚\nit won't be delicious unless we're together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かった……愛には、教えられることばかりだ\n絶対に見つけような、『DENSETSU』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get it… Ai has so much to teach me\nMust find‚ \"DENSETSU\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1697263083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、{user}さん！\n何があってもこの手……離しませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ {user}-san!\nNo matter what happens… I won't let go of this hand!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8666659038,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mountain-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5853.2892546,
          "startTime": 81.7199551584
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――しばらく経ち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After a while",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4866195362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6333325704
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6333325704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……頑張ってここまで来ましたけど\nどうやら私も、限界みたいです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa… I do my best and get this far\nI guess‚ I'm at my limit too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.5666659038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "今、どこにいるのかも分からなくなっちゃいました\n……私達、もう星見プロには帰れないかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ I don't know where I am\n…We may‚ never be able to return to Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "本当にごめんなさい、{user}さんを\n巻き添えにしてしまって……ぐすっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so sorry‚ Looks like\nI got {user}-san involved… sniff",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.4860318186
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いいんだ。愛と『DENSETSU』探しの旅に\n出たことに、後悔なんて……ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. I have no regrets… about joining\nthis journey to find \"DENSETSU\" with AI",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、なんだか疲れたな\n少しだけ……眠らせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ something is tiring\nJust let me sleep… a little",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.840340106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、眠っちゃダメです！\n今眠ったら、きっともう目を覚まさなくなっちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ don't fall asleep!\nIf you fall asleep now‚ you'll never wake up again",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2333325704,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_wind-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5634.556357200012,
          "startTime": 138.8678889276
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.8678889276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　風に乗って何かの匂いが……\nこの脳天を突き刺すようなかぐわしい香りは……豚骨？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? I smell something on the wind…\nThis delicious fragrance that piercing my brain is… tonkotsu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5333305358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.5333305358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "そしてもう一つ、豚骨に負けないふくよかな芳香……\nこれは、幾重にも折り重なった野菜と……煮干し？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And there's another‚ rich fragrance that rivals the tonkotsu…\nThat's‚ layered vegetables and… dried sardines?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9333305358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "私には分かる……この匂いの先に\n『DENSETSU』がある！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can tell… at the end of this smell‚\nthere's \"DENSETSU\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.5999972025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.8531382561
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_52_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ほら、私の背中に……！\n後少しだけ、我慢して下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ come on‚ on my back…!\nPlease hold on‚ just a little longer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4715056756,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
